          div(style="height:70px; text-align:center;")
            p(style="padding-top: 20px; font-size:25px; font-weight:bold") 트랙 진행율
          div(id="chart" style="height:500px; width:200px;")

        .header(style="background:#242930; margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; color:white; box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.19), 0 6px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.23);") Sejong University
